ining two buffers are of type <code dir=3D"auto">CacheOutput</code> and rep=
resent lists of radiance values. The signatures of both the <code dir=3D"au=
to">CacheInput</code> and <code dir=3D"auto">CacheOutput</code> structures =
together with member variables and associated encodings are listed in the t=
